author: Google
description:
Gemini 3 is our most intelligent model to help you with your toughest questions. It brings state-of-the-art reasoning and deep multimodal understanding to unlock dynamic layouts, simulations and interactive tools — all tailored to your specific questions. The experience is now available to everyone in the U.S. in Search, starting with AI Mode when you select the “Thinking with 3 Pro” model from the dropdown menu.

title: Create interactive visuals with Gemini 3 in Google Search

author: Google
description:
Want to make your own custom holiday graphic like this G? Here’s the two-step process:

1️⃣ Open the Google app, press Lens, tap the 🍌, and ask it to “reimagine this [image] fully white made out of snow, floating in front of a Christmas tree outdoors.”
2️⃣ Then Pro/Ultra users can upload the new snowy image to Gemini, select “Create videos (Veo 3.1),” and add the animation prompt: “[image] rotates and returns to the same spot. snow falling.”

#GoogleGemini #GoogleSearch #Veo
title: Easy holiday animation tricks with Search ❄️

author: Google
description: Go beyond simple animation. Veo 3.1 turns prompts into detailed, imaginative video clips. Pro tip: Use descriptive language like “high resolution” and “hyperrealistic.” #GoogleGemini #Veo
title: Unbox your imagination with Veo 3.1 🎁
